rras cuando sea posible;<br>5) fija errores menores<br>______________________________<p>Antigua versiÃ³n 1.2.1:<br>1) Standalone funciÃ³n de exploraciÃ³n<br>2) mÃ¡s opciones para refinar su bÃºsqueda<br>3) posibilidad de codificar muchas informaciones como la direcciÃ³n, el nÃºmero telefÃ³nico, correo electrÃ³nico, URL, ubicaciÃ³n, posiciÃ³n actual, marcadores, eventos del calendario. usted puede compartir toda esta informaciÃ³n a travÃ©s de SMS, correo electrÃ³nico, redes sociales, DLNA, Picasa y otros servicios. <br>________________________</p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p>', '7', '1496812', '0', '0', '0', '2015-03-20 18:35:40', '2015-03-20 18:35:41', '0', '1', '0', '0', 'WB Development Team', null);
INSERT INTO `applications` VALUES ('7', 'at.theengine.android.gesturelauncher', 'Gesture Launcher', '4', '1.3', '3', 'With Gesture Launcher you can launch every application on your device by performing a gesture.<p>USE WIDGET TO START IT TO AVOID DELAY ON START!<p>Just define your own gestures for your most used apps and start them without having to search through the standard app launcher.<p>I wanted to add a widget with a GestureOverlay, but this is not possible, because app widgets do not support this control.<br>But there is a fast starter widget which starts the application a lot faster than a standard shortcut, because it preloads the application list.<p>Project Page: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.google.com/url?q%3Dhttp://wordpress.the-engine.at/gesture-launcher/%26sa%3DD%26usg%3DAFQjCNHW6ccELllzlHA6iAaOs_QyHEwZuQ&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHeup2wYFRwF8o9kqX2weMWGJC0YQ\" target=\"_blank\">http://wordpress.the-engine.at/gesture-launcher/</a></p></p></p></p>', '7', '64703', '0', '0', '0', '2015-03-20 18:34:47', '2015-03-20 18:34:47', '0', '1', '0', '0', 'Bruno Hautzenberger', null);
